#How to Run the CLI version After Downloading the ZIP

#Open the Project Folder in Terminal
Open-Command Prompt / Terminal.
Type the following command to navigate to the project directory:
cd Cli version

#Install Python Dependencies
once you are in the project directory, run the following command to install the required Python libraries:
pip install requests python-dotenv

#Add API Keys in `.env`
Inside `.env` add:
WHOIS_API_KEY=your_key_here
VIEWDNS_API_KEY=your_key_here
SECURITYTRAILS_API_KEY=your_key_here
GENELIFY_API_KEY=your_key_here

#Run the CLI Tool
Run the script:
python main.py

